0public%20and%20even%20contact%20with%20other%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutin's%20long%20been%20rumored%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-children-alina-kabaeva-keeps-them-hidden-in-luxury-report-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20have%20children%20with%20Kabaeva%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20report%20is%20the%20first%20time%20their%20identities%20and%20details%20of%20their%20lives%20have%20been%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20president%20has%20fiercely%20guarded%20details%20of%20his%20private%20life%2C%20but%20is%20known%20to%20have%20two%20daughters%20with%20his%20former%20wife%2C%20Lyudmila%20Putina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20has%20never%20publicly%20confirmed%20their%20identities%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-kids-names-ages-secret-daughters-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey%20are%20said%20to%20be%20Maria%20Vorontsova%2C%20a%20biologist%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Katerina%20Tikhonova%2C%20a%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutin%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20started%20a%20relationship%20with%20Kabaeva%20after%20his%20divorce%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dossier%20Center%20report%20claims%20that%20Ivan%20Putin%20was%20born%20in%202015%20in%20a%20private%20clinic%20in%20Lugano%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20while%20Vladimir%20Jr%20was%20born%20in%202019%20in%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20several%20occasions%2C%20Ivan%20Putin%20told%20his%20tutors%20and%20security%20guards%E2%80%A6that%20when%20he%20was%20born%2C%20Vladimir%20Putin%20was%20so%20happy%20that%20he%20shouted%3A%20'Hurray!%20Finally!%20A%20boy!'%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dossier%20Center%20is%20run%20by%20the%20exiled%20Russian%20opposition%20figure%20Mikhail%20Khodorkovsky%20and%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2F04151c1579724d46a2bda546cb37368d%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublishing%20explosive%20stories%20about%20Putin%20and%20his%20circle%20since%202018%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20latest%20report%20said%20that%20details%20of%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20children%20are%20closely%20guarded%2C%20and%20that%20the%20boys%20have%20used%20%26quot%3Bcover%20documents%20since%20infancy%2C%20which%20are%20mostly%20made%20for%20intelligence%20officers%20and%20people%20under%20state%20protection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Putin%20playing%20hockey%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d995b51d8d2deb96b9197b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20reportedly%20likes%20to%20play%20ice%20hockey%20with%20his%20son%2C%20Ivan.%3Cp%3ESasha%20Mordovets%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20dates%20of%20birth%20are%20known%20only%20to%20their%20closest%20relatives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20lead%20isolated%20lives%20on%20Putin's%20luxury%20estate%20in%20Valdai%2C%20northwest%20of%20Moscow%2C%20where%20they%20are%20surrounded%20by%20tutors%2C%20nannies%2C%20sports%20coaches%2C%20and%20security%20agents%2C%20the%20Dossier%20Center%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmeduza.io%2Fen%2Ffeature%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2Fputin-s-favorite-dacha%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2021%20report%20by%20associates%20of%20Alexander%20Navalny%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Russian%20dissident%20who%20died%20in%20suspicious%20circumstances%20in%20January%2C%20Valdai%20is%20Putin's%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20favorite%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20that%20those%20visiting%20the%20Valdai%20estate%2C%20including%20children%2C%20must%20isolate%20for%20two%20weeks.%20Putin%20himself%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-journalist-putin-isolated-during-pandemic-2022-3%5C%22%20targ