26quot%3Breset%26quot%3B%20before%20matches.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stan%20Wawrinka%20smiled%20and%20poured%20Evian%20water%20into%20a%20glass.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d8c4901d8d2deb96b9051c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWawrinka%20won%20the%202016%20US%20Open%20for%20his%20third-career%20Grand%20Slam%20championship.%3Cp%3EAngela%20Pham%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20USTA%20created%20a%20Mental%20Health%20Initiative%20that%20gave%20players%20access%20to%20quiet%20rooms%2C%20licensed%20mental%20health%20providers%2C%20and%20other%20services%20at%20the%20US%20Open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20Open%20is%20intense%2C%20with%20the%20energy%20from%20the%20crowd%20and%20the%20challenges%20on%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20Wawrinka%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BMentally%20preparing%20is%20just%20as%20crucial%20as%20physical%20training.%20I%20use%20the%20quiet%20rooms%20provided%20to%20reset%20before%20matches%2C%20which%20helps%20me%20focus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Ftimnewcomb%2F2023%2F09%2F01%2Fbehind-the-scenes-us-opens-player-spaces%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20a%20feature%20of%20these%20quiet%20rooms%20is%20beds%2C%20so%20players%20with%20late-night%20matches%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWawrinka%20also%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bstaying%20hydrated%20and%20maintaining%20balance%26quot%3B%20is%20central%20to%20his%20preparation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20USTA%20has%20continued%20to%20highlight%20the%20importance%20of%20mental%20health%20in%20more%20recent%20years.%20At%20the%202023%20US%20Open%2C%20it%20hosted%20the%20%26quot%3BMental%20Health%20and%20Sport%3A%20Why%20It%20Matters%26quot%3B%20panel%20featuring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsi