indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Femergency-the-apprentice-pm-narendra-modi-political-films-that-ran-into-controversy-ahead-of-its-release%2Fphotostory%2F113099078.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20IC-814%20Hijackers%20Demanded%20Terrorist's%20Body%20In%20Exchange%20For%20Hostages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%204.53%20pm%20on%20December%2024%2C%201999%2C%20Indian%20Airlines'%20flight%20IC-814%20took%20off%20from%20Kathmandu%20for%20Delhi.%20A%20two-hour%20long%20flight%20lasted%20almost%20eight%20days%20when%20terrorists%20of%20Pakistan-based%20outfit%20Harkat-ul-Mujahideen%20(HuM)%20hijacked%20the%20Airbus%20A300%20aircraft.%20The%20last%20day%20of%20the%2020th%20century%20was%20indeed%20one%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20for%20the%20then-Atal%20Bihar%20Vajpayee-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Were%20Their%20Demands%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20landed%20in%20Amritsar%2C%20then%20in%20Lahore%2C%20and%20later%20diverted%20to%20Dubai%2C%20finally%20landing%20in%20Taliban-controlled%20Kandahar%20in%20Afghanistan%20on%20December%2025%20at%208%3A33%20am.%20The%20situation%20was%20not%20in%20India's%20control%20and%20it%20was%20time%20for%20negotiation%20with%20the%20hijackers.%20A%20team%20of%20officials%2C%20including%20current%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20from%20relevant%20ministries%20were%20sent%20to%20Afghanistan%20to%20negotiate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen-Foreign%20Minister%20Jaswant%20Singh%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feparlib.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F714070%2F1%2F621.pdf%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20gave%20details%20of%20what%20the%20terrorists%20wanted%20and%20how%20negotiations%20were%20carried%20out.%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Taliban%20advised%20the%20hijackers%20to%20give%20their%20full%20demands%20whereupon%20the%20hijackers%20demanded%20the%20release%20of%2036%20terrorists%20in%20our%20custody%2C%20the%20coffin%20of%20a%20dead%20terrorist%2C%20Sajjad%20Afghani%2C%20and%20a%20sum%20of%20US%20%24200%20million.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20made%20the%20demands%20public%20and%20the%20Taliban%20advised%20the%20hijackers%20that%20demands%20for%20money%20and%20the%20coffin%20of%20Sajjad%20Afghani%20were%20un-Islamic.%20They%20changed%20the%20deal%20and%20insisted%20that%20Masood%20Azhar%20be%20released%20in%20exchange%20for%2015%20hostages%2C%20a%20demand%20which%20was%20again%20rejected%20by%20the%20negotiators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20their%20final%20demands%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20first%20formal%20demand%20made%20by%20the%20hijackers%20to%20our%20officials%20in%20Kandahar%20was%20the%20release%20of%20terrorist%20Masood%20Azhar%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20release%20of%2010%20Indians%20and%205%20foreign%20hostages.%20This%20piecemeal%20approach%20was%20rejected%20by%20the%20Government.%20Both%20the%20Taliban%20and%20the%20hijackers%20were%20informed%20that%20until%20there%20was%20a%20full%20and%20unambiguous%20detailing%20of%20demands%2C%20there%20could%20be%20no%20talks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Was%20Sajjad%20Afghani%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESajjad%20Afghani%20was%20the%20commander-in-chief%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22no%20index%2C%20no%20follow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20191023064529%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.rediff.com%2Fnews%2F1999%2Fdec%2F28afgani.htm%5C%22%3EHarkat%20ul-Ansar%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20was%20killed%20during%20a%20jailbreak%20attempt%20in%20the%20high-security%20Kot%20Balwal%20Jail%20in%20Jammu%20in%20July%201999.%20Afghani%20along%20with%20other%20terrorists%20had%20dug%20a%2023-foot%20tunnel%20inside%20a%20cell%2C%20a%20few%20more%20feet%20and%20they%20would've%20escaped%20but%20the%20prison%20guards%20managed%20to%20catch%20them%20and%20Afghani%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20clash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Masood%20Azhar%20was%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20Harkat%20ul-Ansar.%20Afghani%20and%20Azhar%20were%20arrested%20in%201994.%20Both%20were%20in%20the%20same%20barracks%20from%201997%20in%20Kot%20Balwal%20Jail%20in%20Jammu%20after%20Azhar%20was%20shifted%20from%20Tihar%20Jail%20in%20Delhi%20to%20Jammu.%C2%A0%20His%20body%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20police%20to%20Gujjar%20Nagar%20in%20Jammu%20and%20locals%20buried%20him%20in%20the%20main%20graveyard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20did%20he%20matter%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22no%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.satp.org%2Fsatporgtp%2Fcountries%2Findia%2Fstates%2Fjandk%2Fterrorist_outfits%2Fharkat_ul_ansar_or_harkat_ul_jehad_e_islami.htm%5C%22%3EHarkat%20ul-Ansar%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20formed%20by%20the%20merger%20of%20two%20Pakistan-based%20terror%20outfits%2C%20Harkat%20ul-Jihad%20al-Islami%20and%20Harkat%20ul-Mujahedin.%20The%20merger%20of%20the%20two%20groups%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Afghan%20Jihad.%20It%20happened%20at%20a%20time%20when%20a%20civil%20war%20broke%20out%20in%20Afghanistan%20following%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20Soviets%20and%20radical%20Islamist%20groups%20wanted%20to%20gain%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20found%20success%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Sajjad%20Afghani%20played%20a%20central%20role%20in%20its%20operations.%20Reports%20say%20around%2060%25%20of%20its%201%2C000-strong%20cadre%20were%20Pakistani%20and%20Afghans.%20The%20Indian%20Armed%20Forces%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20succeeded%20in%20capturing%20its%20top%20leaders%20-%20Maulana%20Masood%20Azhar%20Alvi%2C%20Sajjad%20Afghania%20and%20Nasarullah%20Manzoor%20Langaryal%20(Commander%20of%20Harkat%20ul%20Mujahideen).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl-Faran%20kidnapped%20four%20foreigners%20in%20Delhi%20to%20bargain%20the%20release%20of%20Harkat%20ul-Ansar%20leaders.%20But%20the%20plan%20failed%20and%20Delhi%20police%20arrested%20Ahmed%20Omar%20Saeed%20Sheikh%2C%20a%20British%20student%20of%20Pakistani%20origin%20who%20was%20released%20during%20the%20Kandahar%20hijack.%20Omar%20Sheikh%20killed%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal's%20Daniel%20Pearl%20in%202002.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20had%20put%20a%20ban%20on%20Harkat%20ul-Ansar%20for%20its%20associations%20with%20Osama%20bin%20Laden%20in%201997.%20The%20ban%20made%20foreign%20funding%20difficult%20and%20the%20outfit%20was%20renamed%20Harkat%20ul-Mujahideen.%20The%20hijackers%20onboard%20IC-814%20were%20members%20of%20the%20same%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaulana%20Masood%20Azhar%2C%20Mushtaq%20Zargar%20and%20Omar%20Sheikh%20were%20released%20from%20jail%20to%20secure%20the%20passengers%20onboard%20IC-814.%20Masood%20Azhar%2C%20the%20dreaded%20terrorist%2C%20went%20on%20to%20form%20Jaish-e-Mohammed%2C%20the%20outfit%20behind%20the%202001%20Parliament%20attack%2C%202016%20Uri%2C%202019%20Pulwama%2C%202008%20Mumbai%20attacks%20and%20several%20other%20incidents%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20He%20reportedly%20received%20funding%20and%20backing%20from%20Osama%20and%20Pakistan's%20ISI.%20Masood%20Azhar%20was%20also%20the%20mentor%20of%20Omar%20Saeed%20Sheikh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Security%20Adviser%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22no%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fisi-backed-kandahar-hijackers-plane-crisis-negotiator-doval%2Farticleshow%2F56550843.cms%5C%22%3EAjit%20Doval%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20a%20Special%20Director%20in%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20and%20was%20part%20of%20the%20negotiating%20team%20said%20that%20the%20Indian%20Airlines%20flight%20IC-814%20hijackers%20were%20actively%20supported%20by%20the%20ISI%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20they%20had%20not%20got%20support%20from%20the%20ISI%2C%20India%20could%20have%20got%20the%20hijacking%20vacated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKandahar%20was%20Osama's%20fortress.%20Even%20though%20the%20Taliban%20was%20in%20power%20Opium%20and%20money%20laundering%20were%20key%20assets%20of%20revenue%20for%20the%20Taliban%20regime.%20Helmand%20and%20Kandahar%2C%20the%20two%20provinces%20controlled%20the%20trade%20and%20Osama%20Bin%20Laden's%20Al%20Qaeda%20ran%20a%20parallel%20administration%20in%20the%20province.%20Harkat%20ul-Mujahideen%20had%20links%20in%20the%20past%20with%20Osama%20and%20Kandahar%20was%20a%20haven%20for%20the%20terrorists%20to%20negotiate.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725544620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F9tjruor_ic-814-hijack_625x300_05_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhen-ic-814-hijackers-demanded-terrorists-body-in-exchange-for-hostages-6498279%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20Airlines'%20Airbus%20A300%20took%20off%20from%20Kathmandu%20at%204%3A53%20pm%20on%20December%2024%2C%201999%2C%20for%20Delhi.%20A%20two-hour%20long%20flight%20lasted%20for%20almost%20eight%20days%20when%20terrorists%20from%20Pakistan-based%20outfit%20Harkat-ul-Mujahideen%20(HuM)%20hijacked%20the%20aircraft.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhen-ic-814-hijackers-demanded-terrorists-body-in-exchange-for-hostages-6498279%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20found%20out%20my%203-year-old%20daughter%20would%20have%20active%20shooter%20drills.%20I%20pulled%20her%20out%20of%20in-person%20learning%20because%20of%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Unrecognizable%20Daughter%20Being%20Taken%20To%20School%20By%20Her%20Mother%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d9b7e75444ffafa7626727%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222251%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(not%20pictured)%20decided%20to%20pull%20her%20daughter%20out%20of%20preschool%20when%20she%20learned%20about%20active%20shooter%20drills.%3Cp%3Eminiseries%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20my%20daughter%20was%203%20years%20old%2C%20I%20pulled%20her%20out%20of%20preschool%20%E2%80%94%20after%20learning%20of%20shooter%20drills.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20is%20a%20sensitive%20child%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20she'd%20be%20too%20afraid%20to%20learn%20anything.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20American%20Academy%20of%20Pediatrics%20suggests%20schools%20avoid%20high-intensity%20drills.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20pulled%20my%203-year-old%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearly-education-expert-what-parents-teach-kids-before-pre-school-2022-9%5C%22%3Ein-person%20preschool%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20I%20couldn't%20let%20a%20place%20of%20learning%20implant%20visions%20of%20violence%20in%20a%20child%20so%20young%20she%20didn't%20even%20know%20the%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter%20is%20sensitive.%20I%20knew%20she'd%20be%20negatively%20affected%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnumber-of-mass-shootingsin-america-this-year-2022-5%5C%22%3Eshooter-response%3C%2Fa%3E%20drills%2C%20and%20she%20already%20felt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fparenting%2Fhow-to-help-kids-with-anxiety%5C%22%3Eanxious%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20school%2C%20a%20new%20environment%20for%20her.%20If%20she%20was%20afraid%2C%20she%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20absorb%20what%20she%20was%20there%20to%20learn%2C%20whether%20that%20was%20letters%2C%20numbers%2C%20or%20how%20to%20listen%20during%20lockdowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20didn't%20want%20to%20normalize%20violence%20for%20her%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20hesitant%20to%20withdraw%20her%20from%20public%20school%20so%20early%20in%20her%20education%20but%20felt%20the%20intensity%20of%20these%20drills%20would%20be%20harmful%20to%20her%20development.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20normalize%20in%20her%20young%20mind%20threats%20of%20shootings.%20Because%20she's%20a%20child%20already%20prone%20to%20worrying%2C%20I%20couldn't%20expose%20her%20to%20the%20long-term%20effects%20of%20that%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeirdre%20Myers%2C%20a%20residential%20therapist%20with%20the%20Bay%20Area%20Women's%20Center%20in%20Michigan%2C%20told%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BYoung%20children%20are%20unable%20to%20understand%20the%20differences%20between%20drills%20and%20reality%2C%20but%20developing%20secure%20attachments%20with%20teachers%20could%20aid%20with%20following%20instructions%20in%20the%20case%20of%20an%20active%20shooter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20drills%20are%20conducted%20in%20classrooms%20across%20the%20US%20every%20day.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feverytownresearch.org%2Freport%2Fthe-impact-of-active-shooter-drills-in-schools%2F%5C%22%3EForty%20states%20mandate%3C%2Fa%3E%20some%20type%20of%20active-shooter-response%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20local%20district%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alicetraining.com%2F%5C%22%3EALICE%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20for-profit%20facilitator%20of%20active-shooter%20training.%20ALICE%20stands%20for%20%26quot%3Balert%2C%20lockdown%2C%20inform%2C%20counter%2C%20evacuate.%26quot%3B%20The%20program%20would%20have%20exposed%20my%20preschooler%20to%20mock%20shots%20and%20taught%20her%20barricading%20practices%20and%20strategies%20for%20distracting%20shooters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20most%20concerned%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bcounter%26quot%3B%20step%20of%20the%20training.%20This%20step%20directs%20students%20to%20use%20combat%20tactics%20on%20an%20adult%20with%20a%20gun.%20It%20has%20kids%20running%20chaotically%20in%20a%20zigzag%20pattern.%20I%20taught%20my%20child%20to%20remain%20calm%20in%20emergencies%2C%20so%20this%20lesson%20contradicted%20what%20she%20knew.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI'm%20not%20the%20only%20one%20who%20thinks%20drills%20at%20this%20age%20are%20unnecessary%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublications.aap.org%2Faapnews%2Fnews%2F7243%3Fautologincheck%3Dredirected%3FnfToken%3D00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Academy%20of%20Pediatrics%20advises%20against%20these%20kinds%20of%20drills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20national%20certifying%20agency%20for%20shooter-response-training%20organizations.%20I%20was%20far%20from%20convinced%20this%20was%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKadesha%20Adelakun%2C%20a%20registered%20child-play%20therapist%20and%20the%20owner%20of%20The%20Journey%20Counseling%20Services%20in%20Georgia%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BChildren%20can%20be%20indirectly%20traumatized%20by%20the%20simulation%20of%20an%20active%20shooting.%20They%20can%20become%20more%20fearful%20of%20being%20shot%20at%20school%20but%20also%20around%20their%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wrote%20a%20letter%20on%20behalf%20of%20my%20community%20to%20the%20school%20board.%20I%20requested%20exemptions%20for%20kids%20with%20disabilities%2C%20kids%20with%20special%20needs%2C%20kids%20with%20limited%20English-speaking%20ability%2C%20and%20kids%20with%20existing%20traumas.%20I%20asked%20the%20board%20to%20divert%20the%20funds%20from%20the%20drills%20into%20adding%20more%20counselors.%20But%20it%20never%20responded%2C%20and%20I%20began%20to%20question%20the%20value%20system%20of%20our%20schools.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20pulled%20my%20daughter%20out%20of%20preschool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmergencies%20and%20safety%20are%20things%20my%20daughter%20could%20comprehend.%20I%20explained%20to%20her%20that%20just%20as%20we%20practiced%20for%20emergencies%20at%20home%2C%20they%20practiced%20for%20emergencies%20at%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20talk%20about%20shooter%20drills%20in%20age-appropriate%20ways%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20perceptive%20and%20understanding%20but%20had%20a%20few%20questions%20about%20why%20the%20school%20wasn't%20safe.%20It%20was%20difficult%20to%20frame%20it%20in%20an%20age-appropriate%20and%20honest%20way.%20I%20focused%20on%20reassuring%20her.%20I%20told%20her%20it%20was%20my%20job%20to%20protect%20her%2C%20including%20her%20brain%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20let%20her%20be%20in%20a%20situation%20that%20seemed%20unsafe%20for%20her%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%20my%20daughter%20is%208.%20She's%20spent%20only%20two%20months%20in%20the%20public%20school%20system.%20She's%20never%20attended%20an%20active-shooter%20drill%2C%20and%20she's%20never%20been%20involved%20in%20an%20active-shooter%20scenario.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20schooling%20options%20are%20an%20ongoing%20conversation%20now%20that%20she's%20older.%20So%20far%2C%20she%20has%20no%20interest%20in%20attending%20a%20traditional%20school%2C%20and%20she%20has%20no%20idea%20that%20sometimes%20people%20get%20shot%20there.%20She's%20enrolled%20in%20a%20virtual%20school%20that%20holds%20live%20classes%2C%20has%20a%20robust%20curriculum%2C%20and%20conducts%20no%20drills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kid's%20safety%20is%20my%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-pulled-kid-out-of-school-because-active-shooter-drills-2022-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725544500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d9b7e75444ffafa7626727%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-pulled-kid-out-of-school-because-active-shooter-drills-2022-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20my%20daughter%20was%203%20years%20old%20I%20learned%20she%20was%20going%20to%20have%20active%20shooter%20drills.%20As%20a%20sensitive%20child%2C%20I%20didn't%20think%20it'd%20be%20good%20for%20her.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Colleen%20Kelly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-pulled-kid-out-of-school-because-active-shooter-drills-2022-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%2