yber%20Fraud%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20phenomenal%20growth%20in%20the%20digital%20domain%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20has%20also%20brought%20with%20it%20new%20challenges%20in%20cybersecurity%2C%20ISRO%20Chairman%20Dr%20S%20Somanath%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20scientist%20said%20he%20is%20no%20different%20from%20anyone%20else%20in%20receiving%20spam%20calls%20and%20other%20attempts%20at%20fraud.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20never%20been%20a%20victim%20of%20cyber%20fraud%2C%20luckily%2C%20due%20to%20having%20awareness%20and%20knowledge%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%20not%20a%20victim%2C%20but%20there%20were%20lots%20of%20attempts%2C%20like%20all%20of%20you%20would%20have%20faced%2C%20like%20telephone%20calls...%20None%20of%20them%20succeeded%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Somanath%20told%20NDTV%20to%20a%20question%20on%20cyber%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20of%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20the%20cybersecurity%20facility%20called%20'Cyber%20Nalanda'%20in%20Bengaluru.%20It%20is%20the%20brainchild%20of%20SISA%2C%20a%20global%20forensics-driven%20cybersecurity%20solutions%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20growth%20in%20the%20digital%20domain%20in%20India%20is%20really%20phenomenal.%20In%20the%20last%20few%20years%20we%20have%20seen%20the%20growth%20of%20digital%20payment%20infrastructure%2C%20use%20of%20digital%20infrastructure%20for%20education%20and%20learning%2C%20even%20in%20trade%20and%20commerce.%20Related%20to%20that%20cybercrimes%20are%20also%20growing.%20So%20it's%20a%20two-pronged%20approach.%20One%2C%20you%20need%20to%20increase%20the%20digital%20ecosystem.%20And%20two%2C%20you%20need%20to%20handle%20threats%20which%20are%20mostly%20from%20outside%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Somanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20national%20requirement%20to%20strengthen%20cybersecurity.%20It%20also%20happens%20in%20the%20private%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20the%20upcoming%20facility%20has%20been%20named%20'Cyber%20Nalanda'%2C%20Dr%20Somanath%20said%20it%20will%20work%20as%20a%20research%20and%20development%20ecosystem%20in%20cybersecurity%20through%20collaboration%20with%20other%20partners%20and%20academic%20institutions%2C%20and%20Nalanda%20was%20where%20collaboration%20of%20ideas%20used%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatellite%20Launch%20Market%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ISRO%20chief%20said%20the%20space%20agency%20is%20working%20on%20building%20giant%20rockets%20to%20send%20heavier%20satellites%20into%20space.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20Dr%20Somanath%20said%2C%20the%20satellite%20launch%20market%20is%20a%20very%20demanding%20one%20due%20to%20the%20world%20not%20having%20enough%20rockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20There%20are%20not%20enough%20rockets%20in%20the%20world.%20There%20are%20more%20satellites%20than%20rockets.%20But%20then%20the%20launch%20market%20is%20a%20geopolitical%20thing.%20It%20is%20not%20the%20numbers%20alone%20that%20matters.%20But%20the%20cost%2C%20political%20influence%2C%20regional%20demands%2C%20all%20of%20these%20matters.%20So%20we%20are%20trying%20our%20best%20to%20build%20more%20rockets%20and%20make%20them%20available%20for%20commercial%20ventures%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20demand%20for%20small%20satellites%2C%20that's%20why%20a%20lot%20of%20startups%20are%20working%20on%20this.%20In%20the%20middle%20level%2C%20we%20have%20PSLV%2C%20which%20is%20doing%20very%20well.%20In%20the%20high%20level%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20enough%20capability.%20We%20are%20trying%20to%20develop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20he%20feels%20about%20ISRO's%20upcoming%20major%20launches%2C%20Dr%20Somanath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20nervousness%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725542220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22