al%20has%20found%20a%20crucial%20document%20showing%20that%20former%20principal%20Sandip%20Ghosh%20gave%20instructions%20to%20the%20state%20public%20works%20department%20(PWD)%20to%20conduct%20renovation%20in%20areas%20adjacent%20to%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20crime%20a%20day%20after%20victim's%20body%20was%20recovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20of%20the%20victim%20was%20recovered%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20August%209%20from%20the%20seminar%20room%20within%20the%20hospital%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20investigating%20officials%20secured%20a%20crucial%20document%20showing%20that%20Ghosh%20issued%20the%20permission%20letter%20to%20state%20PWD%20to%20conduct%20renovation%20work%20in%20a%20room%20and%20toilet%20adjacent%20to%20the%20seminar%20hall%2C%20which%20is%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigating%20officials%20have%20accessed%20that%20permission%20letter%20which%20bears%20the%20signature%20of%20Ghosh%20and%20is%20dated%20August%2010%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20initially%20it%20was%20perceived%20that%20the%20instruction%20to%20PWD%20to%20start%20the%20renovation%20work%20was%20given%20by%20an%20administrative%20official%20of%20RG%20Kar%20under%20the%20instruction%20of%20Ghosh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20accessing%20the%20permission%20letter%20it%20is%20clear%20how%20keen%20Ghosh%20was%20in%20getting%20the%20renovation%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2013%20evening%2C%20just%20hours%20after%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20ordered%20CBI%20to%20take%20over%20the%20rape%20and%20investigation%20probe%20from%20Kolkata%20Police%2C%20the%20state%20PWD%20staff%20attempted%20the%20renovation%20work%20at%20a%20room%20adjacent%20to%20the%20seminar%20hall%20from%20where%20the%20body%20of%20the%20victim%20was%20recovered%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20August%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that%20renovation%20work%20could%20no