%20rebel%20trouble%20for%20BJP%20started%20shortly%20after%20it%20came%20out%20with%20the%20first%20list%20of%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20quitting%20the%20party%2C%20Mr%20Napa%20met%20former%20chief%20minister%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20and%20later%20said%20he%20will%20be%20joining%20the%20Congress%20along%20with%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjit%20Chautala%20called%20a%20meeting%20of%20his%20supporters%20after%20the%20party%20ignored%20his%20candidature%20from%20Rania%20segment%20in%20Sirsa%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20took%20the%20decision%20after%20consulting%20my%20supporters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20his%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20good%20relations%20with%20them%20(BJP).%20They%20gave%20me%20Lok%20Sabha%20ticket%20(from%20Hisar%2C%20which%20he%20fought%20unsuccessfully).%20But%20don't%20know%20on%20whose%20advice%20they%20have%20acted.%20I%20will%20say%20anyone%20who%20has%20given%20them%20this%20advice%20has%20caused%20damage%20to%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chautala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20Chaudhary%20Devi%20Lal's%20son.%20I%20have%20some%20stature...%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20contest%20as%20an%20Independent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20while%20adding%20he%20has%20resigned%20as%20minister%20and%20quit%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chautala%20was%20hoping%20to%20contest%20from%20Rania%20seat%20but%20the%20BJP%20fielded%20Shishpal%20Kamboj%20instead.%C2%A0He%20had%20resigned%20as%20Independent%20MLA%20from%20Rania%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%20and%20fought%20the%20Hisar%20parliamentary%20seat%20unsuccessfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Napa%2C%20sitting%20MLA%20from%20Ratia%20reserve%20constituency%20in%20Fatehabad%20district%2C%20said%20he%20served%20his%20constituency%20with%20full%20dedication%20and%20undertook%20development%20works.%20He%20said%20he%20does%20not%20know%20why%20the%20party%20denied%20him%20re-nomination%20from%20the%20assembly%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Napa%20said%20he%20had%20met%20Mr%20Hooda%20Thursday%20morning.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20joining%20the%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20minister%20Karan%20Dev%20Kamboj%20said%20he%20has%20resigned%20as%20state%20president%20of%20Haryana%20BJP's%20OBC%20Morcha%20and%20from%20all%20party%20posts%20he%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kamboj%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20ticket%20hopeful%20but%20did%20not%20get%20it%2C%20said%20he%20had%20been%20serving%20the%20party%20over%20the%20years%20with%20dedication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerhaps%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20need%20loyalists%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20party%20is%20rewarding%20leaders%20with%20tickets%20who%20joined%20a%20day%20before%20while%20ignoring%20those%20who%20served%20it%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20sitting%20legislators%2C%20including%20minister%20Sanjay%20Singh%20and%20former%20minister%20Sandeep%20Singh%2C%20do%20not%20figure%20in%20the%20first%20list%20of%20BJP%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Ratia%2C%20the%20party%20has%20fielded%20former%20Sirsa%20MP%20Sunita%20Duggal.%20In%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Ms%20Duggal%20was%20denied%20re-nomination%20from%20the%20Sirsa%20parliamentary%20constituency%20after%20former%20Haryana%20Congress%20chief%20Ashok%20Tanwar%2C%20who%20had%20joined%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%20LS%20polls%2C%20was%20given%20the%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tanwar%2C%20however%2C%20lost%20to%20Congress%20veteran%20Kumari%20Selja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Haryana%20minister%20and%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Kavita%20Jain%2C%20a%20ticket%20hopeful%20from%20Sonipat%2C%20was%20also%C2%A0%20reportedly%20sulking%20after%20party%20fielded%20Nikhil%20Madan%20from%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20her%20supporters%20in%20Soni