A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%20had%20initially%20said%20he%20would%20not%20contest%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20But%20he%20joined%20the%20fray%20at%20the%20last%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20he%20had%20explained%20his%20change%20of%20heart%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20if%20I%20believe%20I%20am%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20then%20I%20must%20lead%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20the%20assembly%2C%20he%20said%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bhypocritical%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bseen%20as%20hypocritical%26quot%3B%20if%20he%20were%20to%20tell%20people%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20believe%20in%20this%20assembly%2C%20but%20you%20must%20vote%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20the%20flaws%20of%20this%20assembly%2C%20it%20is%20still%20better%20than%20what%20we%20have%20now.%20This%20assembly%20may%20not%20be%20the%20assembly%20that%20it%20was%20in%202018%2C%20but%20it%20is%20still%20an%20assembly%20that%20will%20speak%20for%20them%20that%20will%20fight%20for%20their%20rights.%20And%20also%20this%20is%20an%20assembly%20that%20will%20bring%20back%20the%20statehood%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20We'll%20make%20a%20start%20from%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%2090-member%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly%20after%20a%20decade%20on%20September%2018%2C%20September%2025%20and%20October%201.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20take%20place%20on%20October%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725534780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Ft83htf7_omar-abdullah-budgam_625x300_05_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-ganderbal-omar-abdullah-files-nomination-from-budgam-6497150%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20National%20Conference%20chief%20Omar%20Abdullah%20has%20filed%20a%20second%20nomination%20to%20contest%20the%20assembly%20polls%20from%20Budgam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-ganderbal-omar-abdullah-files-nomination-from-budgam-6497150%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20AAP%20Alliance%2C%20No%20CM%20Face%3A%20Decoding%20Congress's%20Haryana%20Strategy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-01%2Fdqh52igg_congress-generic_625x300_21_January_20.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20Haryana%20assembly%20elections%2C%20which%20will%20be%20held%20on%20October%205%20with%20results%20announced%20on%20October%208.%20The%20party%20is%20finalising%20its%20candidate%20list%20and%20has%20decided%20not%20to%20announce%20a%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%2C%20opting%20instead%20for%20a%20combined%20leadership%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20resumed%20talks%20with%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20regarding%20a%20potential%20alliance.%20Although%20the%20two%20previously%20contested%20the%202024%20general%20elections%20together%2C%20early%20indications%20suggested%20they%20would%20go%20their%20own%20ways%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConfident%20after%20its%20strong%20performance%20in%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20where%20it%20matched%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20with%20five%20seats%20each%2C%20the%20Congress%20believes%20it%20has%20a%20good%20chance%20in%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20led%20in%2044%20assembly%20segments%2C%20the%20Congress%20in%2042%2C%20and%20the%20AAP%20in%20four.%20In%20terms%20of%20vote%20share%2C%20the%20BJP%20received%2046%25%2C%20the%20Congress%2044%25%2C%20and%20the%20AAP%204%25%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20CM%20Face%20to%20Curb%20Factionalism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20CEC%20meeting%20on%20Monday%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Ajay%20Singh%20Yadav%20announced%20that%20the%20party%20would%20not%20project%20a%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Haryana%20assembly%20elections.%20The%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20chief%20ministership%20will%20be%20made%20by%20the%20high%20command%20after%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20emphasised%20that%20defeating%20the%20BJP%20should%20be%20the%20priority%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20He%20noted%20that%20the%20party's%20National%20General%20Secretary%20(Organization)%20Sandeep%20Pathak%20would%20engage%20in%20talks%20with%20Congress%20if%20the%20proposal%20gained%20momentum.%20%26quot%3BThe%20final%20decision%20will%20be%20made%20by%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP's%20Haryana%20chief%2C%20Sushil%20Gupta%2C%20stated%20his%20personal%20opinion%20that%20the%20party%20should%20not%20settle%20for%20four%20to%20five%20seats%20but%20left%20the%20final%20decision%20to%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20National%20Convenor%20Kejriwal.%20Reports%20also%20indicate%20that%20AAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20is%20involved%20in%20back-channel%20negotiations%20with%20Congress%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EAppealing%20To%20Broad%20Groups%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20former%20Haryana%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupender%20Singh%20Hooda%20is%20leading%20the%20Congress%20effort%2C%20but%20a%20faction%20including%20Kumari%20Selja%20and%20Randeep%20Surjewala%20is%20reportedly%20unhappy%20with%20Hooda%20consolidating%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKiran%20Choudhury%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20this%20faction%2C%20left%20the%20party%20for%20the%20BJP%20after%20her%20daughter%20was%20denied%20a%20ticket%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20decision%20to%20not%20announce%20a%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20move%20to%20curb%20factionalism%20and%20appeal%20to%20a%20broader%20electorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20strategy%20aims%20to%20avoid%20a%20Jat%20versus%20non-Jat%20contest.%20The%20Congress%2C%20under%20Hooda's%20leadership%2C%20is%20perceived%20as%20representing%20Jat%20interests.%20The%20BJP%20has%20exploited%20Jat%20versus%20non-Jat%20dynamics%20to%20its%20advantage%20in%20previous%20polls.%20Congress%20is%20focusing%20on%20a%20coalition%20of%20Jats%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20Muslims.%20Dalits%2C%20who%20make%20up%2020%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20are%20crucial.%20Kumari%20Selja's%20role%20as%20a%20Dalit%20face%20and%20the%20non-announcement%20of%20a%20CM%20candidate%20help%20maintain%20hope%20within%20the%20Dalit%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20CSDS%20post-poll%20study%2C%2064%25%20of%20Jats%20and%2068%25%20of%20Dalits%20voted%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20Congress%20hopes%20this%20decision%20will%20help%20retain%20the%20majority%20of%20Dalit%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPossible%20Alliance%20With%20AAP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress-AAP%20alliance%20performed%20well%20in%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20winning%20five%20seats%20and%20securing%20a%2048%25%20vote%20share.%20Although%20AAP%20contested%20the%20Kurukshetra%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20and%20lost%2C%20it%20led%20in%20four%20assembly%20segments%20and%20garnered%20a%204%25%20vote%20share.%20The%20AAP's%20solo%20run%20could%20split%20the%20opposition%20vote%20and%20potentially%20benefit%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20aims%20to%20avoid%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%202019%20scenario%20when%20the%20Jannayak%20Janata%20Party%20(JJP)%2C%20led%20by%20Dushyant%20Chautala%2C%20seemingly%20spoiled%20its%20chances.%20The%20JJP's%2010%20seats%2C%20largely%20from%20Jat-dominated%20areas%2C%20hurt%20the%20Congress's%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20parties%20initially%20planned%20to%20go%20solo%2C%20but%20last-minute%20discussions%20at%20the%20high%20command%20level%20revived%20talks.%20The%20AAP%20is%20reportedly%20demanding%2010%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20is%20currently%20offering%20two%20to%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bania%20community%2C%20comprising%204%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20Aroras%2FPunjabis%2FKhatris%20(7%25)%2C%20and%20Sikhs%20(5%25)%20are%20significant%20demographics%20in%20Haryana.%20The%20AAP%20has%20pockets%20of%20influence%20among%20these%20groups%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20gain%20some%20support%20in%20Haryana%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20led%20in%2019%20of%2023%20urban%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20led%20in%20only%20four.%20In%20rural%20Haryana's%2060%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20led%20in%2034%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%2022.%20The%20AAP%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20considerable%20influence%20in%20urban%20areas%2C%20particularly%20those%20bordering%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%2C%20where%20Congress's%20weak%20seats%20are%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20strategy%20allows%20Congress%20to%20focus%20on%20strengthening%20its%20position%20in%20its%20strong%20Jat-dominated%20region%20while%20leveraging%20AAP's%20influence%20in%20weaker%20areas%20to%20maximise%20gains%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725534480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A