%26quot%3B%2C%20killings%20and%20vandalism%20must%20be%20investigated%2C%20identified%20and%20punished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20good%20for%20us%20or%20for%20India.%20There%20is%20discomfort%20regarding%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20unprecedented%20anti-government%20protests%20that%20peaked%20on%20August%205%2C%20Hasina%20resigned%20as%20prime%20minister%20and%20fled%20to%20India.%20Her%20presence%20in%20India%20for%20nearly%20four%20weeks%20has%20fuelled%20speculation%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20Bangladesh%20has%20communicated%20its%20stance%20to%20India%2C%20Yunus%20said%20it%20has%20been%20conveyed%20verbally%20and%20quite%20firmly%20that%20she%20should%20keep%20quiet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbangladesh-violence-quota-protests-5-more-murder-cases-filed-against-sheikh-hasina-total-cases-now-71-report-6430267%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%205%20More%20Murder%20Cases%20Against%20Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%20Total%20Count%20Now%2071%3A%20Report%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20understands%20it.%20We%20have%20said%20quite%20firmly%20that%20she%20should%20keep%20quiet.%20This%20is%20an%20unfriendly%20gesture%20towards%20us%3B%20she%20has%20been%20given%20shelter%20there%20and%20she%20is%20campaigning%20from%20there.%20It%20is%20not%20that%20she%20has%20gone%20there%20on%20a%20normal%20course.%20She%20has%20fled%20following%20a%20people's%20uprising%20and%20public%20anger%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%20stated%20that%20the%20interim%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20justice%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Bangladesh%20against%20the%20atrocities%2C%20and%20justice%20requires%20that%20she%20be%20brought%20back%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20she%20has%20to%20be%20brought%20back%20or%20else%20the%20people%20of%20Bangladesh%20won't%20be%20at%20peace.%20The%20kind%20of%20atrocities%20she%20has%20committed%2C%20she%20has%20to%20be%20tried%20in%20front%20of%20everyone%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20the%20future%20of%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20relationship%2C%20Yunus%20expressed%20a%20desire%20for%20good%20ties%20with%20India%20but%20insisted%20that%20New%20Delhi%20must%20abandon%20the%20narrative%20that%20only%20Hasina's%20leadership%20ensures%20the%20country's%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20forward%20is%20for%20India%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20narrative.%20The%20narrative%20is%20that%20everybody%20is%20Islamist%2C%20the%20Bangladesh%20Nationalist%20Party%20(BNP)%20is%20Islamist%2C%20and%20everyone%20else%20is%20Islamist%20and%20will%20make%20this%20country%20into%20Afghanistan.%20And%20Bangladesh%20is%20in%20safe%20hands%20with%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20at%20the%20helm%20only.%20India%20is%20captivated%20by%20this%20narrative.%20India%20has%20to%20come%20out%20of%20this%20narrative.%20Bangladesh%2C%20like%20any%20other%20nation%2C%20is%20another%20neighbour%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20recent%20incidents%20of%20alleged%20attacks%20on%20Hindu%20minorities%20in%20the%20country%20and%20India%20raising%20concerns%20about%20it%2C%20Yunus%20said%20this%20is%20just%20an%20excuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20issue%20of%20trying%20to%20portray%20the%20conditions%20of%20minorities%20in%20such%20a%20big%20way%20is%20just%20an%20excuse%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minority%20Hindu%20population%20has%20faced%20vandalism%20of%20their%20businesses%20and%20properties%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20destruction%20of%20Hindu%20temples%2C%20during%20the%20student-led%20violence%20that%20erupted%20following%20the%20ouster%20of%20Hasina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20his%20Independence%20Day%20address%20from%20the%20ramparts%20of%20the%20Red%20Fort%20on%20August%2015%2C%2