of%20his%20recent%20releases%20(%3Cem%3EBeast%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ELeo)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20hero%20comes%20out%20of%20years%20of%20living%20in%20the%20shadows%20and%20returns%20to%20the%20thick%20of%20the%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20deadpan%20throwbacks%20to%20the%20megastar's%20own%20films%20and%20stray%20nods%20to%20other%20Tamil%20movies%20and%20songs%20that%20place%20him%20in%20the%20larger%20context%20of%20mass%20cinema%20history%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Greatest%20of%20All%20Time%3C%2Fem%3E%20perhaps%20contains%20a%20meta-allusion%20to%20the%20upcoming%20end%20of%20the%20Vijay%20acting%20career%20in%20preparation%20for%20a%20plunge%20into%20full-time%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FjxCRlebiebw%3Fsi%3DkMB23HkG69AOU0su%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Greatest%20of%20All%20Time%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eseeks%20to%20extend%20Vijay's%20uninterrupted%20run%20of%20box-office%20successes%20-%20a%20string%20of%20nine%20blockbusters%20has%20made%20him%20Indian%20cinema's%20most%20bankable%20actor.%20The%20film%20has%20everything%20that%20his%20fans%20crave.%20What%20it%20could%20have%20done%20with%20is%20a%20more%20original%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20juggles%20with%20themes%20that%20have%20been%20done%20to%20death%20-%20friendship%2C%20loyalty%2C%20betrayal%2C%20guilt%20and%20redemption%20-%20and%20culminates%20in%20a%20long-drawn-out%20climax%20that%20pits%20two%20personas%20of%20the%20actor%20against%20each%20other.%20Beyond%20the%20parameters%20of%20the%20fictional%20narrative%2C%20one%20could%20interpret%20the%20confrontation%20as%20one%20between%20a%20generation%20gone%20by%20and%20an%20era%20carrying%20a%20baggage%20that%20blurs%20the%20line%20between%20good%20and%20bad%2C%20between%20sense%20of%20duty%20and%20the%20need%20for%20self-preservation%20and%20vengeance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20plays%20M.S.%20Gandhi%20-%20note%20that%20the%20initials%20aren't%20MK%2C%20but%20MS.%20The%20Dhoni%20parallel%20comes%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20the%20film's%20climax%2C%20which%20corresponds%20with%20a%20make-or-break%20last%20over%20of%20an%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20knockout%20fixture%20at%20a%20packed-to-the-rafters%20Chepauk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20-%20peace%20isn't%20his%20primary%20weapon%2C%20righteousness%20is%20-%20leads%20a%20quartet%20of%20secret%20agents%20who%20work%20for%20the%20Special%20Anti-Terror%20Squad%20(SATS)%2C%20a%20Chennai-based%20unit%20of%20RAW.%20He%20is%20the%20MSD%20of%20Indian%20espionage%20-%20a%20great%20finisher%20no%20matter%20how%20badly%20he%20starts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20true%20of%20the%20film%2C%20too.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Greatest%20of%20All%20Time%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0opens%20with%20a%20bang%20all%20right%20but%20loses%20its%20way%20somewhat%20through%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20first%20half%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20achieve%20a%20balance%20between%20the%20hero's%20innate%20bellicosity%20and%20familial%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20himself%20suggests%2C%20he%20has%20two%20bosses%2C%20one%20at%20the%20workplace%2C%20a%20rock-steady%20SATS%20chief%20Nazeer%20(Jayaram)%2C%20and%20another%20at%20home%2C%20his%20wife%20Anusuya%20(Sneha).%20He%20gets%20into%20trouble%20far%20more%20with%20the%20latter%20than%20the%20former.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20series%20of%20crucial%20reveals%20and%20a%20string%20of%20killings%20by%20a%20duplicitous%20young%20man%20who%20surfaces%20from%20Gandhi's%20past%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Greatest%20of%20All%20Time%3C%2Fem%3E%20makes%20it%20way%20to%20an%20unoriginal%20finale%20that%20is%20salvaged%20somewhat%20by%20the%20flair%20with%20which%20it%20is%20mounted%20and%20filmed.%20Cinematographer%20Siddhartha%20Nuni%20and%20editor%20and%20Venkat%20Raajen%20deserve%20a%20mention%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20devastating%20bomb%20blast%20is%20only%20a%20press%20of%20a%20button%20away.%20Gandhi%2C%20trained%20never%20to%20flinch%2C%20is%20determined%20to%20demonstrate%20who%20the%20GOAT%20is.%20He%20swings%20into%20action%20as%20thousands%20of%20innocent%20lives%20hang%20in%20the%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20-%20Gandhi%20works%20alongside%20Kalyan%20Sundaram%20(Prabhu%20Deva)%2C%20Sunil%20Thiagarajan%20(Prasanth)%20and%20Ajay%20(Ajmal%20Ameer)%20-%20is%20sent%20on%20a%20sensitive%20mission%20to%20Kenya.%20They%20waylay%20a%20train%20carrying%20weapons-grade%20uranium%20meant%20for%20a%20terrorist%20outfit.%20In%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20they%20end%20of%20exceeding%20their%20brief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ill-advised%20overreach%20-%20it%20does%20not%20yield%20the%20desired%20result%20-%20returns%20to%20haunt%20Gandhi%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20their%20five-year-old%20son%20Jeevan%20(Akhil)%20-%20and%20his%20SATS%20associates.%20In%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20intermission%2C%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20boss%20are%20drawn%20into%20a%20violent%20clash%20with%20a%20man%20who%20hides%20his%20face%20behind%20a%20crash%20helmet%20that%20has%20'Devil'%20written%20under%20the%20visor.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remainder%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Greatest%20of%20All%20Time%3C%2Fem%3E%20hinges%20on%20a%20renegade%20secret%20agent%20(who%20has%20a%20massive%20axe%20to%20grind%20and%20lets%20loose%20unending%20bedlam)%20and%20sundry%20other%20traitors%20and%20prodigals%20who%20push%20the%20protagonist%20and%20his%20men%20to%20the%20end%20of%20their%20tether.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20is%20at%20times%20a%20touch%20exhausting%20because%20it%20is%20overlong.%20However%2C%20the%20action%20sequences%20and%20plot%20twists%20are%20judiciously%20spaced%20out%20over%20a%20three-hour%20runtime.%20So%2C%20none%20of%20them%20is%20unduly%20out%20of%20place.%20Wish%20one%20could%20say%20the%20same%20about%20the%20songs%20(composed%20by%20Yuvan%20Shankar%20Raja).%20They%20not%20only%20slow%20down%20the%20film%20but%20also%20stretch%20it%20out%20unconscionably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20director%2C%20on%20his%20part%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20effect%20that%20the%20musical%20numbers%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20on%20the%20pace%20of%20the%20film.%20In%20a%20sequence%20that%20follows%20the%20cold-blooded%20murder%20of%20a%20government%20official%2C%20the%20perpetrator%20uses%20his%20romantic%20interest%20(Meenakshi%20Chaudhary)%20as%20a%20means%20to%20shake%20off%20the%20pursuer.%20Is%20this%20what%20you%20called%20me%20here%20for%2C%20the%20lady%20asks.%20No%2C%20(I%20called%20you%20here)%20for%20a%20song%2C%20the%20man%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20thriller%20such%20as%20this%2C%20action%20is%20the%20principal%20currency.%20Every%20song%20isn't%20music%20to%20the%20ear.%20Similarly%2C%20not%20every%20attempt%20that%20the%20film%20makes%20to%20inject%20humour%20into%20the%20proceedings%20bears%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogi%20Babu%20is%20thrown%20in%20as%20a%20man%20who%20is%20in%20possession%20of%20a%20stolen%20mobile%20phone%20that%20contains%20crucial%20secrets.%20Taking%20off%20from%20the%20name%20of%20the%20hero%2C%20Nehru%20and%20Bose%20are%20evoked%20by%20the%20sub-plot%20to%20shore%20up%20a%20stretch%20of%20the%20film%20that%20does%20not%20quite%20add%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%2C%20fleshing%20out%20two%20distinct%20characters%2C%20one%20greying%20and%20steely%2C%20the%20other%20callow%20and%20obdurate%2C%20and%20both%20carrying%20scars%20past%20events%2C%20makes%20up%20for%20whatever%20the%20film%20lacks%20in%20terms%20of%20logic%20and%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20the%20sort%20of%20rescue%20act%20that%20he%20has%20pulled%20off%20so%20often%20this%20millennium%20that%20it%20has%20stopped%20surprising%20his%20critics.%20His%20fans%2C%20of%20course%2C%20will%20find%20no%20reason%20to%20feel%20shortchanged%20with%20what%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Greatest%20of%20All%20Time%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20generous%20proportions.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725530640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Ffqht9kjo_vijay-_625x300_05_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fthe-greatest-of-all-time-review-vijay-carries-the-film-on-his-shoulders-2-5-stars-6496579%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20review%20is%20of%20the%20original%20Tamil%20version%20of%20the%20film%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fthe-greatest-of-all-time-review-vijay-carries-the-film-on-his-shoulders-2-5-stars-6496579%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Leave%20Parents%20Alone'%3A%20Trinamool%20On%20'Money%20Offer'%20To%20Kolkata%20Doctor%20Family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20massive%20row%20over%20the%20serious%20allegations%20by%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20doctor%2C%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20at%20a%20state-run%20hospital%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20today%20blamed%20%26quot%3Bvulture%20politics%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Opposition%20and%20doubled%20down%20on%20the%20charge%20that%20fake%20narratives%20are%20being%20created.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20video%20has%20gone%20viral%20and%20it%20suggests%20that%20the%20parents%20were%20offered%20money%20by%20the%20police%20to%20hush%20up%20the%20case.%20In%20another%20video%2C%20the%20parents%20have%20said%20this%20allegation%20is%20false.%20They%20said%20they%20only%20want%20justice%20for%20their%20daughter.%20They%20are%20heart-broken.%20There%20should%20have%20been%20no%20politics%20here.%20Political%20parties%20should%20not%20bother%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20state%20minister%20Shashi%20Panja%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20massive%20row%20has%20erupted%20after%20the%2031-year-old%20doctor's%20parents%20told%20the%20media%20yesterday%20that%20the%20police%20offered%20them%20money%20when%20their%20daughter's%20body%20was%20still%20at%20their%20home.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20this%20money%20was%20offered%20as%20a%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Trinamool%20supporters%20started%20sharing%20another%20video%2C%20in%20which%20the%20parents%20are%20asked%20if%20they%20were%20offered%20money%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20hush%20up%20the%20case.%20%26quot%3BNothing%20like%20this%20happened%2C%20we%20just%20want%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20are%20heard%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20today%20played%20the%20second%20video%20at%20their%20press%20meet%20and%20said%20the%20CBI's%20silence%20on%20the%20progress%20of%20its%20investigation%20has%20created%20a%20vacuum%20in%20which%20fake%20news%20and%20narratives%20are%20being%20manufactured.%20%26quot%3BLeading%20this%20fake%20news%20creation%20is%20BJP%20and%20its%20IT%20cell%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20earlier%20seen%20much%20talk%20about%20the%20post-mortem%20report%20too...%20sensational%20claims%20like%20150%20gm%20semen%2C%20this%20is%20injustice%20towards%20the%20victim.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwenty-three%20days%20have%20passed%20after%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20case%20from%20Kolkata%20Police%20to%20CBI.%20There%20is%20no%20progress%20report%20from%20CBI.%20We%20demand%20that%20the%20CBI%20provide%20a%20detailed%20progress%20report%20of%20their%20investigation.%20When%20Kolkata%20police%20was%20investigating%20this%2C%20regular%20updates%20were%20given%20out%20through%20press%20conferences%2C%26quot%3B%20state%20minister%20Bratya%20Basu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20party%2C%20which%20is%20under%20fire%20over%20the%20shocking%20incident%2C%20questioned%20if%20the%20CBI%20has%20nothing%20in%20the%20rape-murder%20case%20apart%20from%20what%20Kolkata%20Police%20handed%20over.%20It%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20central%20agency's%20investigation%20appears%20to%20have%20shifted%20from%20the%20rape-murder%20to%20financial%20irregularities%2C%20in%20which%20connection%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20former%20principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20was%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20has%20alleged%20that%20evidence%20was%20wiped%20off%2C%20why%20is%20CBI%20not%20coming%20out%20then%20and%20saying%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Basu%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20leaders%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20other%20allegations%20levelled%20by%20the%20victim's%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctor's%20family%20has%20alleged%20that%20they%20wanted%20the%20body%20preserved%2C%20but%20police%20created%20so%20much%20pressure%20that%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20cremation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20the%20body%20preserved%2C%20but%20so%20much%20pressure%20was%20created.%20About%20300-400%20cops%20surrounded%20us.%20We%20returned%20home%20and%20found%20some%20300%20cops%20were%20standing%20outside.%20They%20created%20such%20a%20situation%20that%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20cremate%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%20He%20also%20said%20the%20cremation%20was%20rushed%20and%20the%20cost%20was%20not%20taken%20from%20the%20family.%20%26quot%3BMy%20daughter%20went%20knowing%20that%20Bapi%20(father)%20could%20not%20even%20pay%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20victim's%20father%20said.%20He%20also%20alleged%20that%20some%20police%20officers%20tried%20to%20get%20his%20signature%20on%20a%20blank%20sheet%20of%20paper.%20%26quot%3BI%20tore%20it%20up%20and%20threw%20it%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20have%20targeted%20the%20Trinamool%20over%20the%20father's%20allegations%20and%20said%20the%20police's%20role%20in%20the%20case%20has%20been%20exposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MLA%20Agnimitra%20Paul%20said%20the%20parents'%20interaction%20with%20the%20media%20last%20night%20has%20%26quot%3Bexposed%20the%20role%20of%20Kolkata%20Police%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20YOU%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20tried%20to%20suppress%20this%20case%20and%20protect%20the%20conspirators%20and%20deviate%20the%20direction%20of%20this%20case.%20You%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20answer%20the%20people%20of%20Bengal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725530460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fjken5fi8_kolkata-protest_625x300_05_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-leave-parents-alone-trinamool-on-money-offer-to-kolkata-doctor-family-6496566%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20massive%20row%20over%20the%20serious%20allegations%20by%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20doctor%2C%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20at%20a%20state-run%20hospital%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20today%20blamed%20%26quot%3Bvulture%20politics%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Opposition%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-leave-parents-alone-trinamool-on-money-offer-to-kolkata-doctor-family-6496566%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20India%20Is%20Finally%20Reversing%20Its%20Semiconductor%20Misfortune%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fcefisvro_semiconductor_625x300_05_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(This%20is%20the%20second%20article%20in%20a%20two-part%20series%20on%20the%20US-China%20semiconductor%20battle%2C%20and%20where%20India%20stands%20in%20it.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fchina-is-eating-away-at-uss-tech-reign-chip-by-chip-6481939%5C%22%3EHere%20is%20the%20first%20part%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Chandrayaan%203%20landed%20on%20the%20moon%20on%20August%2023%20last%20year%2C%20there%20was%20one%20place%20in%20Mohali%20that%20was%20particularly%20jubilant%3A%20the%20government-run%20Semiconductor%20Laboratory%20(SCL).%20It%20was%20a%20personal%20win%20for%20SCL's%20engineers%2C%20the%20unsung%20heroes%20who%20for%20months%20worked%20on%20producing%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20semiconductors%20critical%20for%20controlling%20and%20commanding%20the%20mission.%20The%20spacecraft%20used%20chips%20to%20enable%20communication%20with%20Earth%20and%20navigate%20its%20way%20to%20the%20landing%20destination%2C%20using%20sensors%20and%20cameras%20to%20transmit%20data%20and%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohali's%20SCL%20is%20India's%20only%20well-known%20chip-making%20foundry.%20It%20began%20production%20in%201984%2C%20three%20years%20before%20the%20world's%20biggest%20semiconductor%20manufacturing%20company%2C%20the%20Taiwan%20Semiconductor%20Manufacturing%20Company%20(TSMC)%2C%20was%20founded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20however%2C%20while%20TSMC%20produces%2090%25%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20sophisticated%20and%20advanced%20semiconductors%20or%20microchips%2C%20churning%20out%20the%20most%20valued%205-nanometer%20(nm)%20chips%20in%20size%2C%20SCL%20can%20make%20only%20legacy%20chips%20of%20100%20nm%20and%20above%2C%20which%20are%20obviously%20many%20generations%20old.%20TSMC's%20annual%20turnover%20exceeded%20%2470%20billion%20last%20year%2C%20far%20more%20than%20the%20SCL's%20meagre%20%245%20million.%20And%20while%20TSMC's%20clients%20are%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20leading%20tech%20firms%2C%20such%20as%20Apple%2C%20AMD%20and%20Nvidia%2C%20among%20SCL's%20top%20clients%20is%20just%20ISRO%20(Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation).%20TSMC's%20factories%20are%20state-of-the-art%3B%20SCL%20is%20in%20dire%20need%20of%20modernisation%20and%20upgradation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Tough%20Luck%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESCL%20could%20have%20been%20TSMC's%20largest%20rival%20if%20it%20were%20not%20for%20one%20very%20unfortunate%20incident%2C%20which%20pushed%20India%20back%20to%20the%20semiconductor%20dark%20ages.%20On%20February%2027%2C%201989%2C%20a%20mysterious%20fire%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20plant%2C%20destroying%20most%20of%20the%20facilities.%20To%20date%2C%20no%20one%20knows%20if%20it%20was%20an%20act%20of%20sabotage%20or%20an%20accident.%20The%20factory%20later%20rose%20from%20the%20ashes%2C%20but%20by%20then%2C%20it%20was%20left%20far%20behind%20in%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDan%20Hutcheson%20of%20Canada's%20TechInsights%20company%2C%20one%20of%20the%20industry's%20global%20voices%2C%20surprised%20me%20when%20he%20said%20he%20had%20been%20monitoring%20the%20Indian%20chip%20industry%20since%20the%201970s.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20seen%20India%20strive%20for%20this%20industry%20my%20entire%20career.%20There%20have%20been%20only%20failures.%20It%20is%20important%20for%20India%20to%20be%20successful%20now.%26quot%3B%20Dan%20is%20not%20wrong%2C%20as%20India's%20semiconductor%20history%20is%20made%20up%20of%20a%20series%20of%20broken%20dreams%20and%20unfulfilled%20promises.%20Several%20multinational%20companies%20tried%20their%20luck%20in%20setting%20up%20chip%20production%20projects%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20materialise%20for%20various%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMicron%20Project%2C%20A%20Sign%20Of%20Good%20Things%20To%20Come%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20India%20over%20three%20decades%20after%20the%201989%20tragedy%20to%20see%20a%20positive%20development%20in%20its%20semiconductor%20journey.%20In%20August%20last%20year%2C%20a%20groundbreaking%20ceremony%20was%20held%20in%20Sanand%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20for%20Micron%20Technology's%20state-of-the-art%20semiconductor%20assembly%2C%20testing%2C%20and%20packaging%20facility.%20Its%20bosses%20claim%20the%20facility%20will%20be%20operational%20early%20next%20year.%20The%20plant%20will%20be%20completed%20in%20two%20phases%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20%242.75%20billion%20%E2%80%93%20%24825%20million%20being%20invested%20by%20Micron%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20by%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Gujarat%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Micron%20project%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20country's%20bright%20chip%20future.%20Since%20the%20groundbreaking%20ceremony%C2%A0last%20year%2C%20four%20new%20projects%20have%20been%20announced%2C%20the%20latest%20on%20Monday%20when%20the%20government%20said%20it%C2%A0cleared%20a%20proposal%20of%20Kaynes%20Semicon%20to%20set%20up%20a%20semiconductor%20unit%20in%20Sanand.%20All%20the%20new%20units%2C%20except%20Tata%20Electronics'%20fab%20unit%20in%20Dholera%20in%20Gujarat%20are%20testing%20and%20packaging%C2%A0units.%20Taiwain's%20Powerchip%20Semiconductor%20Manufacturing%20Corporation%20(PSMC)%20and%20Tata%20Electronics%20announced%20in%C2%A0February%20this%20year%20that%20they%20will%20set%20up%20a%20fabrication%20unit%20in%20Dholera.%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20government%20will%20be%20more%20keen%20to%20see%20the%20progress%20of%20this%20project%20because%20it's%20India's%20first%20fab%20unit%20in%20the%20private%20sector.%20Neither%20company%20in%20their%20press%20statements%20have%C2%A0given%20a%20completion%20date%20or%20the%20costs%20involved%20but%20according%20to%20media%C2%A0reports%2C%20the%20total%20project%20will%20cost%20Rs%2091%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20witnessed%20several%20false%20dawns%20in%20the%20last%20few%20decades%2C%20but%20now%20things%20appear%20to%20be%20changing%2C%20and%20at%20a%20fast%20speed.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20India%20could%20not%20even%20dream%20of%20producing%20sophisticated%20smartphones.%20That%20was%20a%20domain%20exclusively%20captured%20by%20China.%20Today%2C%20India%20is%20a%20manufacturing%20hub%20for%20iPhones%20and%20other%20smartphone%20brands.%20Citing%20this%20success%20story%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20last%20year%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20successfully%20made%20India%20a%20manufacturing%20hub%20for%20mobile%20phones%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%20Now%2C%20our%20next%20goal%20is%20to%20position%20the%20country%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20semiconductor%20manufacturing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Is%20Established%20In%20Just%20One%20Segment%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20semiconductor%20manufacturing%20ecosystem%20requires%20infrastructure%20for%20designing%2C%20fabrication%2C%20research%2C%20testing%2C%20and%20packaging.%20Besides%2C%20it%20needs%20sophisticated%20tools%2C%20minerals%2C%20and%20gases%20to%20make%20chips.%20While%20India%20severely%20lacks%20large-scale%20semiconductor%20fabrication%20facilities%2C%20it%20has%20built%20a%20robust%20ecosystem%20for%20chip%20design%20and%20related%20services.%20Major%20global%20semiconductor%20companies%20such%20as%20Intel%2C%20Qualcomm%2C%20Texas%20Instruments%2C%20NVIDIA%2C%20AMD%20and%20Broadcom%20have%20established%20significant%20design%20and%20R%26amp%3BD%20centres%20in%20India.%20Indian%20engineers%20contribute%20to%20the%20design%20of%20the%20most%20complex%20chips%20used%20in%20cutting-edge%20technologies%2C%20from%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%205G%20networks.%20Companies%20like%20Wipro%2C%20Tata%20Elxsi%2C%20and%20HCL%20Technologies%20also%20provide%20outsourced%20semiconductor%20design%20services%2C%20catering%20to%20global%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BLearn%20To%20Walk%20Before%20You%20Can%20Run%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20wants%20India%20to%20become%20a%20fabrication%2C%20R%26amp%3BD%2C%20testing%2C%20and%20packaging%20hub.%20A%20tall%20order%20indeed%2C%20considering%20India%20is%20only%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20chip%20race%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20an%20impossible%20one.%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%20several%20industry%20experts%20worldwide%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20and%20they%20believe%20India%20can%20become%20a%20semiconductor%20hub%20and%20a%20global%20player%20in%2010-20%20years%20if%20it%20stays%20as%20focused%2C%20patient%2C%20and%20committed%20as%20the%20Modi%20government%20appears%20to%20be%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20India's%20efforts%20in%20perspective%2C%20we%20ought%20to%20remember%20that%20it%20took%20semiconductor%20superpowers%20Taiwan%20and%20South%20Korea%20decades%20to%20reach%20where%20they%20are%20in%20the%20race%20today.%20%26quot%3BRealistically%2C%20it'll%20take%2010%20to%2020%20years%2C%20assuming%20it%20is%20well-executed.%20You%20have%20to%20learn%20to%20walk%20before%20you%20can%20run.%20That's%20the%20important%20thing%20%E2%80%93%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20Micron%20project%20is%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Hutcheson%2C%20who%20calls%20the%20Micron%20packaging%20project%20%26quot%3Ba%20great%20baby%20step%E2%80%9D.%20To%20be%20sure%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20and%20China%20all%20started%20with%20packaging%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChip%20fabrication%2C%20which%20allows%20for%20the%20production%20of%205%20nm%20or%20even%202%20nm%20microchips%2C%20is%20widely%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20key%20to%20the%20success%20of%20a%20semiconductor%20mission.%20A%20host%20of%20things%20are%20needed%20before%20manufacturing%20can%20start%2010-15%20years%20later.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20simple%20industry%3B%20it%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20and%20high-end%20equipment%20and%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Investment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Semiconductor%20Industry%20Association%20estimates%2C%20a%20state-of-the-art%20manufacturing%20factory%20takes%20a%20minimum%20of%2010%20years%20to%20produce%20chips.%20The%20initial%20capital%20investment%20and%20operating%20costs%20can%20run%20up%20to%20anywhere%20between%20%2410%20billion%20and%20%2440%20billion.%20If%20India%20dreams%20of%20being%20a%20chi%20hub%2C%20it%20will%20have%20to%20invest%20hugely%20in%20the%20sector%20in%20the%20next%2010-15%20years.%20China%20has%20been%20doing%20just%20that%2C%20pouring%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20becoming%20self-reliant%20in%20semiconductor%20manufacturing.%20The%20US%20has%20pumped%20in%20over%20%24100%20billion%20in%20its%20own%20industry%20since%202022.%20Against%20these%20stark%20figures%2C%20India%20has%20managed%20to%20inject%20just%20about%20%2415%20billion%20into%20its%20semiconductor%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20India%20badly%20needs%20is%20private%20investors%20and%20global%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Gases%20and%20Mineral%20Shortages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESemiconductor%20chip%20manufacturing%20essentially%20uses%20more%20than%20150%20types%20of%20chemicals%20and%20over%2030%20types%20of%20gases%20and%20minerals.%20At%20present%2C%20all%20these%20are%20available%20only%20in%20a%20few%20countries.%20The%20challenge%20for%20India%20is%20to%20be%20self-reliant%20in%20this%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Supporting%20Industries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20believe%20that%20the%20main%20task%20for%20India%20is%20to%20create%20supporting%20industries%20for%20the%20chip%20industry%20to%20emerge.%20The%20issue%20relates%20to%20some%20basic%20things%2C%20like%20having%20a%20stable%20power%20grid%20and%20consistent%20water%20availability%2C%20which%20make%20it%20possible%20to%20build%20the%20semiconductor%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Political%20Will%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chip%20industry%20is%20capital-intensive%20and%20time-consuming%2C%20which%20requires%20deep%20commitment%20from%20the%20government%20and%20private%20players%20alike.%20It%20requires%20the%20willpower%20of%20successive%20governments%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20game.%20PM%20Modi%20wants%20India%20to%20be%20a%20developed%20economy%20by%202047.%20A%20long-term%20semiconductor%20strategy%20will%20be%20needed%20if%20India%20really%20is%20to%20become%20a%20developed%20country%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Skilled%20Manpower%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20manpower%20in%20abundance%2C%20but%20it%20has%20a%20shortage%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20skilled%20manpower%20needed%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Brain%20Drain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20could%20achieve%20its%20goal%20of%20becoming%20a%20semiconductor%20hub%20in%20around%20five%20to%20six%20years%20rather%20than%20the%20conventional%2010-20%20year%20timeframe%20if%20we%20manage%20to%20bring%20big%20Indian%20talent%2C%20serving%20global%20companies%2C%20back%20home.%20Can%20we%20entice%20them%20with%20equivalent%20salary%20packages%20and%20perks%3F%20Can%20nation-building%20be%20a%20motivator%3F%20Can%20we%20improve%20our%20work%20culture%20to%20make%20it%20more%20professional%20and%20productive%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaiwan's%20success%20story%20owes%20a%20lot%20to%20the%20Taiwanese-origin%20executives%20who%20obtained%20their%20semiconductor%20expertise%20and%20experiences%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20Taiwanese%20government%20in%20the%201980s%20decided%20to%20bring%20its%20talented%20people%20back%20to%20kickstart%20the%20semiconductor%20industry.%20It%20paid%20them%20salaries%20on%20a%20par%20with%20Western%20companies.%20These%20expat%20Taiwanese%20played%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20making%20Taiwan%20a%20truly%20global%20chip%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea's%20chip%20revolution%20also%20started%20after%20the%20government%20enticed%20many%20Korean%20experts%20working%20in%20Japanese%20companies%20to%20come%20back%20and%20work%20in%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20dearth%20of%20Indians%20who%20are%20doing%20well%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20business%20in%20the%20US%20and%20elsewhere.%20Around%20a%20dozen%20leaders%20of%20the%20world's%20leading%20chip-making%20companies%20are%20either%20Indian%20or%20of%20Indian%20origin.%20I%20have%20met%20a%20couple.%20They%20all%20love%20India.%20But%20India%20needs%20to%20create%20the%20right%20conditions%20to%20bring%20them%20back%2C%20and%20also%20stop%20the%20brain%20drain%20of%20young%20engineering%20graduates%20who%20are%20in%20high%20demand%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20New%20Dawn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20sealing%20deals%20with%20several%20multinational%20companies%20to%20launch%20new%20projects.%20The%20Modi%20government%20has%20recognised%20the%20fact%20that%20if%20India%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20big%20geopolitical%20player%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20the%20leading%20light%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20arena.%20What%20follows%20after%20the%20Micron%20factory%20will%20determine%20the%20future%20of%20India's%20semiconductor%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725530400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fkdi4q9t8_semiconductor_625x300_05_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-is-finally-reversing-its-semiconductor-misfortune-6496509%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Modi%20government%20has%20recognised%20the%20fact%20that%20if%20India%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20big%20geopolitical%20player%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20the%20leading%20light%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20arena.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3