20to%20win%20the%202024%20US%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fvladimir-putin-says-he-wants-infectious-kamala-harris-to-win-us-election-over-donald-trump-13209969%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fvladimir-putin-says-he-wants-infectious-kamala-harris-to-win-us-election-over-donald-trump-13209969%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fvladimir-putin-says-he-wants-infectious-kamala-harris-to-win-us-election-over-donald-trump-13209969%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Investor%20Who%20Risked%20It%20All%20On%20'Black%20Myth%3A%20Wukong'%20Now%20Minting%20Millions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBlack%20Myth%3A%20Wukong%20has%20sold%2018%20million%20copies%20in%20two%20weeks%20-%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20starts%20the%20global%20gaming%20industry%20has%20seen.%20That%20record%20pace%20has%20in%20turn%20minted%20millions%20for%20its%20earliest%20and%20biggest%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWukong%20was%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20for%20Daniel%20Wu%2C%20whose%20little-known%20Hero%20Games%20is%20the%20biggest%20external%20shareholder%20in%20creator%20Game%20Science.%20His%20startup%20stuck%20with%20its%20partner%20through%20years%20of%20flops%20and%20contributed%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20the%20blockbuster%20title's%20%2470%20million%20budget%20over%20six%20years%20of%20development%2C%20an%20unheard-of%20undertaking%20for%20a%20Chinese%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20paid%20off%20big%20time.%20The%20action%20game%20based%20on%20the%20legend%20of%20the%20Monkey%20King%20has%20outsold%20industry%20icons%20such%20as%20Elden%20Ring%20and%20Zelda%2C%20at%20least%20in%20its%20initial%20spurt.%20It%20can%20reach%2030%20million%20sales%20over%20its%20lifetime%2C%20augmented%20with%20an%20expansion%20to%20come%2C%20Wu%20told%20Bloomberg%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20biggest%20PC%20creation%20emerged%20from%20a%20creative%20team%20whose%20biggest%20claim%20to%20fame%20before%20this%20summer%20was%20a%20visit%20from%20Apple%20Inc.'s%20Tim%20Cook.%20Wu%2C%20who%20escorted%20the%20iPhone%20boss%20around%20Hero's%20Shanghai%20offices%20in%202017%2C%20said%20one%20of%20its%20early%20collaborations%20with%20Game%20Science%20caught%20Cook's%20eye%20-%20though%20that%20project%20ultimately%20tanked.%20It%20took%20another%20four%20years%20before%20Tencent%20Holdings%20Ltd.%20invested%20in%20Hero's%20investee%2C%20after%20a%20tantalizing%20Wukong%20trailer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Game%20Science%20is%20worth%20several%20billion%20yuan%2C%20Wu%20said%2C%20marking%20a%20return%20of%20several-fold%20on%20his%20studio's%2020%25%20stake.%20Hero%20Games%20had%20paid%20just%2060%20million%20yuan%20(%248.5%20million)%20for%20its%20slice%20in%202017.%20Both%20startups%20find%20themselves%20unexpectedly%20in%20the%20spotlight%2C%20hailed%20for%20finally%20showing%20China%20is%20capable%20of%20producing%20a%20big-budget%20title%20on%20par%20with%20the%20best%20of%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20hear%20the%20truth%2C%20Game%20Science's%20success%20today%20is%20built%20upon%20its%20four%20failures%20in%20a%20row%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2036-year-old%20Wu%20said%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20from%20his%20Beijing%20office.%20%26quot%3BWukong%20proves%20not%20only%20that%20we%20have%20top-notch%20game-making%20capabilities%2C%20but%20also%20we%20can%20tell%20a%20good%20story%20with%20Chinese%20elements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Wu%2C%20who%20gave%20up%20a%20career%20as%20a%20startup%20financier%20to%20immerse%20himself%20in%20games%20close%20to%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20Wukong%20is%20much%20more%20than%20just%20a%20groundbreaking%20game.%20He%20and%20Game%20Science%20co-founder%20Feng%20Ji%2C%20five%20years%20his%20elder%2C%20tied%20their%20fortunes%20to%20the%20success%20of%20a%20title%20built%20for%20consoles%20and%20PCs%2C%20in%20a%20country%20dominated%20by%20mobile%20entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fhp0nh4oc_hero-games-office-bloomberg_625x300_05_September_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20release%20on%20Aug.%2020%2C%20the%20game%20has%20broken%20several%20records%20for%20single-player%20titles%2C%20eclipsing%20the%20likes%20of%20Cyberpunk%202077%20with%20runaway%20popularity%20at%20home%20in%20China.%20It's%20estimated%20to%20have%20earned%20%24700%20million%20so%20far%2C%20overshadowed%20only%20by%20Call%20of%20Duty's%20historic%20%241%20billion%20in%2010%20days%2C%20according%20to%20Niko%20Partners%20analyst%20Daniel%20Ahmad.%20He%20sees%20overseas%20sales%20accounting%20for%20a%20larger%20share%20going%20forward%20as%20the%20game's%20global%20renown%20grows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWukong%20got%20a%20lift%20from%20state%20media%20lauding%20its%20faithful%20depiction%20of%20historic%20and%20cultural%20sites%2C%20but%20success%20came%20only%20after%20Wu%20and%20Feng%20risked%20everything%20to%20realize%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20two%20drowning%20rats%2C%26quot%3B%20Wu%2C%20whose%20company%20is%20still%20not%20profitable%2C%20said%20of%20himself%20and%20Feng.%20%26quot%3BNeither%20of%20us%20was%20afraid%20of%20failure%2C%20and%20he%20already%20knew%20his%20next%20step.%20The%20only%20thing%20is%20that%20he%20needed%20me%20to%20place%20even%20bigger%20bets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGame%20Science%20had%20struck%20out%20with%20its%20three%20prior%20efforts%2C%20which%20were%20more%20modest%20free-to-play%20mobile%20games%20chasing%20attention%20in%20the%20world's%20biggest%20games%20arena.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20Art%20of%20War%3A%20Red%20Tides%2C%20even%20got%20prime%20placement%20on%20the%20iOS%20App%20Store%20after%20Cook's%20visit%2C%20but%20to%20no%20avail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sole%20investor%20and%20publishing%20partner%20of%20Game%20Science%2C%20Hero%20Games%20took%20significant%20losses%2C%20but%20Wu%20didn't%20shy%20away%20in%202018%20when%20Feng%2C%20now%20his%20late-night%20League%20of%20Legends%20teammate%2C%20reached%20out%20for%20more%20money%20to%20craft%20an%20ambitious%20project%20then%20codenamed%20Black%20Myth%20One.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20won't%20take%20another%20six%20years%20for%20the%20next%20chapter%20in%20what's%20planned%20to%20be%20a%20series%20based%20on%20Chinese%20mythology%20-%20though%20that%20won't%20be%20a%20sequel%2C%20Wu%20said.%20Game%20Science%20is%20working%20on%20an%20expansion%20to%20Wukong%2C%20which%20will%20give%20it%20a%20chance%20to%20monetize%20the%20game%20a%20second%20time.%202022's%20Elden%20Ring%2C%20a%20title%20with%20similar%20play%20style%20and%20design%2C%20has%20shown%20how%20the%20release%20of%20an%20expansion%20-%20this%20year's%20Shadow%20of%20the%20Erdtree%20-%20can%20spur%20a%20fresh%20flurry%20of%20sales%20for%20the%20original.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWu%20co-founded%20Hero%20Games%20in%202015%20after%20a%20three-year%20stint%20with%20famed%20Chinese%20venture%20firm%20ZhenFund.%20He%20zeroed%20in%20on%20Feng%20and%20his%20Game%20Science%20team%20early%20on%2C%20describing%20them%20as%20an%20asset%20he%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20miss%20out%20on.%20At%20Tencent%2C%20Feng%20had%20led%20a%20team%20of%20250%20people%20on%20the%20development%20of%20online%20role-playing%20game%20Asura%2C%20inspired%20by%20similar%20folklore%20to%20Wukong.%20The%20title%20launched%20in%202010%20and%20initially%20won%20praise%20for%20its%20design%2C%20though%20it%20later%20upset%20players%20with%20practices%20around%20its%20in-game%20shop%20that%20were%20deemed%20exploitative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHero%20Games%2C%20which%20orchestrated%20a%20marketing%20blitz%20around%20Wukong%20that%20included%20Luckin%20Coffee%20giveaways%2C%20also%20drew%20criticism%20outside%20of%20China%20for%20its%20guidance%20to%20streamers%20playing%20Wukong%20to%20not%20discuss%20%26quot%3Bfeminist%20propaganda%2C%26quot%3B%20politics%20or%20Covid-19.%20Wu%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202%2C000-person%20Hero%20Games%20team%2C%20even%20with%20that%20huge%20winning%20bet%20in%20its%20portfolio%2C%20isn't%20making%20a%20profit.%20Wu's%20company%20is%20on%20a%20yearslong%20transition%20from%20publisher%20to%20developer%2C%20and%20it's%20facing%20the%20same%20challenges%20that%20Game%20Science%20ran%20into%20when%20trying%20to%20score%20a%20mobile%20hit.%20Until%20it%20breaks%20through%2C%20Wu's%20message%20to%20staff%20this%20year%20will%20be%20to%20learn%20to%20embrace%20the%20death%20of%20your%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20most%20gruesome%20year%20for%20China's%20games%20industry%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20Wu%20said%2C%20noting%20the%20large%20number%20of%20unsuccessful%20games%20that%20few%20will%20ever%20see%20or%20hear%20about.%20The%20country's%20economic%20difficulties%20have%20cut%20into%20entertainment%20spending%20and%20forced%20many%20studios%20to%20reconsider%20or%20abandon%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20makes%20the%20triumph%20of%20Wukong%20all%20the%20sweeter.%20Wu%20expects%20it%20will%20fire%20up%20passions%20and%20interest%20to%20create%20more%20games%20based%20China's%20rich%20history%20and%20culture%20-%20and%20more%20courage%20to%20build%20for%20consoles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Wu%20encountered%20the%20first%20big%20fight%20in%20Wukong%20on%20his%20PlayStation%205%2C%20he%20texted%20Feng%20to%20say%20he%20was%20welling%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20dare%20you%20cry%20without%20me%3F%26quot%3B%20Feng%20texted%20him%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725526980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fm3m23c8_daniel-wu_